CREATE EXTERNAL TABLE [dbo].[ext_FACT_CUSTPACKINGSLIPTRANS] WITH (
        LOCATION = 'FACT_CUSTPACKINGSLIPTRANS/Archive',
        DATA_SOURCE = [eds_tx-halfen-2-dwh],
        FILE_FORMAT = [eff_Csv]  
) AS
SELECT
    *
FROM
    OPENROWSET(
        BULK './FACT_CUSTPACKINGSLIPTRANS/FACT_CUSTPACKINGSLIPTRANS.csv',
        FORMAT = 'CSV', PARSER_VERSION = '2.0',
        FIELDTERMINATOR =';',
        ROWTERMINATOR = '\r',
        HEADER_ROW = TRUE
    ) 
    WITH (
        [DW_Id] bigint,
	    [DATAAREAID] VARCHAR (4) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8,
	    [ORIGSALESID] VARCHAR (20) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8,
	    [PACKINGSLIPID] VARCHAR (20) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8,
	    [DLVCOUNTRYREGIONID] VARCHAR (10) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8,
	    [DELIVERYDATE] DATETIME2 ,
	    [DeliveryDate_RunningDayNumber] bigint ,
	    [HPLDLVMODEID] VARCHAR (10) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8,
	    [INVENTTRANSID] VARCHAR (24) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8,
	    [ITEMID] VARCHAR (20) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8,
	    [INVENTDIMID] VARCHAR (20) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8,
	    [ORDERACCOUNT] VARCHAR (20) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8,
	    [SalesTaker] VARCHAR (20) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8,
	    [DLVTerm] VARCHAR (10) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8,
	    [Payment] VARCHAR (10) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8,
	    [DIMENSION] VARCHAR (10) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8,
	    [HPLCOSTPRICE] VARCHAR (30) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8,
	    [QTY] decimal(38,12) ,
	    [AMOUNTCUR_CZ] decimal(38,12) ,
	    [CURRENCYCODE_CZ] VARCHAR (3) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8,
	    [ShippingSiteRequested_RunningDayNumber] VARCHAR (10) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8,
        [SHIPPINGDATECONFIRMED_tf] VARCHAR (500) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8 ,
        [ShippingDateConfirmed_tf_RunningDayNumber] VARCHAR (500) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8 ,
        [RECID] bigint,
        [INVENTSITEID] VARCHAR (10) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8,
        [INVENTLOCATIONID] VARCHAR (10) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8,
        [DeliveryDateDiff] VARCHAR (10) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8,
        [Reliability01] bigint,
        [DeliveryDateDiff2] VARCHAR (10) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8,
        [Reliability201] bigint ,
        [CategoryId] bigint ,
        [ExtendedCategoryId] bigint ,
        [bomlines] bigint ,
        [SalesLine_Dw_Id] VARCHAR (10) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8,
        [CountryRegion_DW_Id] bigint ,
        [DateKey_DeliveryDate] bigint ,
        [CustPackingslipJour_DW_Id] bigint ,
        [ReqItemTable_DW_Id] VARCHAR (20) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8,
        [SameDeliveryDate_SalesLine] VARCHAR (50) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8,
        [Reliability_Stock_Items] VARCHAR (50) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8,
        [HLFSEGMENTID] VARCHAR (4) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8,
        [Segment_DW_Id] VARCHAR (10) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8,
        [SALESGROUP] VARCHAR (10) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8,
        [SalesPerson_DW_Id] VARCHAR (10) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8,
        [DW_Id_Itemid] bigint ,
        [DW_Batch] bigint ,
        [DW_SourceCode] VARCHAR (15) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8,
        [DW_TimeStamp] DATETIME2
    ) AS [result]
